data.description: PRICE REDUCED $10,000! Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac, this charming 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath residence is the epitome of comfort and style. Boasting a spacious loft and a fenced-in backyard, this home has it all. Step inside to discover a world of updates and amenities that make life here truly special. The kitchen offers granite countertops and two-tone painted cabinets that add a touch of sophistication. Plus, you'll enjoy the modern convenience of a 4 yr old HVAC system (Trane), a Google Nest system, and an ADT Alarm System for peace of mind. The spacious pantry ensures you'll have plenty of storage space for all your culinary adventures. And, as you venture outside, you'll find an outdoor storage building, a charming pergola shading a welcoming patio, and a fire pit for those cozy gatherings with family and friends. This home is not just a house; it's a warm and welcoming haven. It's the perfect place for both entertaining and relaxation.
